ba_jail_cellblock 1st beta by SeriesOfTubes

This is only the beta version, more improvements/updates are expected 
in future releases.

To Install:
put the BSP file in the following path:
C:\Program Files\Steam\Steamapps\[username]\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

Additional Notes:
I've been working on this map for quite some time, and really wanted to release the map.

FEATURES THAT SOME JB MAPS DON'T HAVE!:
Party Room [RAVE PARTY!]
Bombsite
Multi-stop elevator (little buggy)

What to expect in future releases:
Additional rooms for the multi stop elevator
More songs for the party room
3D skybox
Fixes and additions
